\pard\pagebb\keepn\outlinelevel0\sb480\sa240\cf1\fs36\b 1. System Overview\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\qj\sb80\sa80\cf3\fs21 MathAI is a full-stack, AI-powered adaptive mathematics learning platform targeting students from Grade 1 through Grade 8. The platform uses a Turborepo monorepo that houses a Next.js 15 frontend (apps/web), an Express 4.18 API backend (api/), and a shared Prisma database layer (database/). The system is deployed split-stack: the frontend on Vercel and the backend API on Render, with Supabase PostgreSQL as the persistent store.\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
\pard\keepn\outlinelevel1\sb360\sa200\cf2\fs28\b 1.1 Key Capabilities\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Adaptive curriculum engine that generates personalised practice problems per student grade and topic\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Spaced-repetition scheduling via an SM-2-variant algorithm for long-term knowledge retention\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Gamification layer: XP points, streaks, level progression, and achievement badges\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Dual-model AI strategy: claude-haiku-4.5 (fast drill) and claude-sonnet-4.5 (step-by-step hints)\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Google OAuth and email/password authentication via NextAuth.js v4\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Role-based access control: student / teacher / admin\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Admin dashboard for user management, content oversight, and analytics\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
