\pard\keepn\outlinelevel1\sb360\sa200\cf2\fs28\b 6.2 Key Components\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\keepn\outlinelevel2\sb240\sa140\cf9\fs23\b PracticeSession\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\qj\sb80\sa80\cf3\fs21 Manages the full question-answer-feedback loop using a React state machine (idle > question > answering > feedback > next). Integrates the Vercel AI SDK useChat hook for streaming AI tutor messages in a side panel. Framer Motion powers XP award animations on correct answers.\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
\pard\keepn\outlinelevel2\sb240\sa140\cf9\fs23\b AppNav / AdminNav\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\qj\sb80\sa80\cf3\fs21 Role-aware navigation bar. AppNav shows standard student links. AdminNav adds content management and analytics links. Both include a sign-out button wired to NextAuth signOut().\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
\pard\keepn\outlinelevel1\sb360\sa200\cf2\fs28\b 6.3 State Management\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Server state: React Query (useQuery / useMutation) for all API calls\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Global client state: Zustand stores for session progress and user preferences\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Form state: uncontrolled inputs with Zod validation on submit\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
\pard\pagebb\keepn\outlinelevel0\sb480\sa240\cf1\fs36\b 7. AI & Curriculum Engine\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\keepn\outlinelevel1\sb360\sa200\cf2\fs28\b 7.1 Model Configuration\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\qj\sb80\sa80\cf3\fs21 The AI provider is abstracted behind an aiClient factory (api/src/lib/aiClient.ts) controlled by the AI_PROVIDER env var. Two modes are supported:\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  mock \u8212? canned responses; no API key needed; used in local dev and CI\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  anthropic \u8212? routes to Anthropic via @ai-sdk/anthropic\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
