\pard\keepn\outlinelevel1\sb360\sa200\cf2\fs28\b 7.2 Curriculum Engine\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\qj\sb80\sa80\cf3\fs21 practiceMenuService reads StudentProfile.aiAssignedTopics (set at signup by Claude), merges with canonical topics for the student's grade, and applies mastery weights from SpacedRepetitionCard records to surface due-for-review topics first.\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
\pard\keepn\outlinelevel1\sb360\sa200\cf2\fs28\b 7.3 Spaced Repetition (SM-2 Variant)\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\qj\sb80\sa80\cf3\fs21 After each answer the system updates SpacedRepetitionCard: easeFactor is adjusted by performance quality, interval is computed by the SM-2 formula, and nextReviewAt is scheduled accordingly.\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
