\pard\pagebb\keepn\outlinelevel0\sb480\sa240\cf1\fs36\b 10. Security Model\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\keepn\outlinelevel1\sb360\sa200\cf2\fs28\b 10.1 Authentication Security\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  All session tokens are JWE-encrypted (A256CBC-HS512) using NEXTAUTH_SECRET\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Tokens are short-lived (24h) and httpOnly cookies prevent XSS access\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Disabled accounts (isActive: false) are rejected at NextAuth authorize and Express authMiddleware\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Password hashing uses bcrypt cost factor 12\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  INTERNAL_SERVICE_SECRET is a 32-byte cryptographic random value\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
\pard\keepn\outlinelevel1\sb360\sa200\cf2\fs28\b 10.2 API Security\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Helmet.js sets X-Frame-Options, X-Content-Type-Options, Strict-Transport-Security, etc.\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  CORS restricted to CORS_ORIGIN \u8212? no wildcard origins\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  express-rate-limit applies per-IP limits on auth and AI endpoints\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  All request bodies validated with Zod schemas\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  SQL injection prevented by exclusive use of Prisma parameterised queries\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
\pard\keepn\outlinelevel1\sb360\sa200\cf2\fs28\b 10.3 Data Handling\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  No PII is logged; Winston filters email fields from log output\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  .env.local is gitignored and never committed\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  ANTHROPIC_API_KEY is server-side only, never exposed to the browser\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
