\pard\pagebb\keepn\outlinelevel0\sb480\sa240\cf1\fs36\b 12. Operational Runbook\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\keepn\outlinelevel1\sb360\sa200\cf2\fs28\b 12.1 Health Checks\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  API: GET https://mathai-api.onrender.com/api/health \u8212? expect \{status:'ok'\}\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Frontend: https://mathai.aiops.ae \u8212? expect 200 HTML\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Database: Supabase dashboard > Database > Table Editor\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
\pard\keepn\outlinelevel1\sb360\sa200\cf2\fs28\b 12.2 Common Issues\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\keepn\outlinelevel2\sb240\sa140\cf9\fs23\b API Cold Start (Render Free Tier)\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\qj\sb80\sa80\cf3\fs21 Render free tier spins down after 15 minutes of inactivity. First request after cold start can take 30\u8211?60 seconds. Mitigation: configure UptimeRobot to ping /api/health every 14 minutes.\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
\pard\keepn\outlinelevel2\sb240\sa140\cf9\fs23\b Signup 500 Error\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\qj\sb80\sa80\cf3\fs21 Previously traced to an invalid 'grade' field on studentProfile.create. Fixed in commit: fix(signup): remove invalid grade field. If 500 errors recur, check Render logs for Prisma 'Unknown argument' errors.\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
\pard\keepn\outlinelevel2\sb240\sa140\cf9\fs23\b Google OAuth Redirect URI Mismatch\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\qj\sb80\sa80\cf3\fs21 Symptom: 'Error 400: redirect_uri_mismatch' on Google sign-in. Fix: ensure NEXTAUTH_URL=https://mathai.aiops.ae is set on Vercel AND https://mathai.aiops.ae/api/auth/callback/google is registered in Google Cloud Console under Authorised redirect URIs.\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
\pard\keepn\outlinelevel2\sb240\sa140\cf9\fs23\b Database Connection Exhaustion\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\qj\sb80\sa80\cf3\fs21 Always use the Supabase pooler URL (port 6543 with ?pgbouncer=true). The pooler supports up to 200 concurrent clients vs the 20-connection limit on direct connections.\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
\pard\keepn\outlinelevel1\sb360\sa200\cf2\fs28\b 12.3 Monitoring\b0\cf3\fs21\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Render dashboard: real-time logs, resource metrics, deploy history\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Vercel dashboard: build logs, function invocation metrics, edge network status\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Supabase dashboard: query performance, storage usage, auth logs\par
\pard\sb60\sa60\li360\fi-180\cf3\fs21 \bullet  Winston logs (API): structured JSON with level, message, userId, path, duration\par
\pard\sb0\sa120\par
